子登機證，以此通過安全檢查和移民署並登上中華航空飛航之航班。"},{"pid":"ffb13a6d6d393a4ba0d6c5cdfffa7bc04fac9da3","tid":760140,"uid":95881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acab967042210bc32722494ce99669a05c2faec1","tid":760140,"uid":95881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c9ea7180c7a3aef7bd089634ac298bf7c4239a6","tid":760140,"uid":27397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a76005a57e7c09c9c4f3f2fb7067a3e8969a558d","tid":760140,"uid":95881,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T11:22:08.000Z","msg":"唔同公司<br />\n唔同機場<br />\n有唔同做法"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T11:33:00.000Z","msg":"中華航空<br />\n香港機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T11:39:46.000Z","msg":"官網一定有寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中華航空電子登機證<br />\n中華航空於2012年3月26日起，推出電子登機證服務，旅客經由華航網站、CI Mobile APP 辦理預辦登機(eCheck-In)手續後，可在手持式行動裝置(如智慧型手行動電話)上收到電子登機證，以此通過安全檢查和移民署並登上中華航空飛航之航班。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T11:41:05.000Z","msg":"直接show qr code就得<br />\n登機前會叫名check passport"},{"pid":"21776cd04b61f7c2e42dfd6ebea878a16a79887b","tid":760140,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T11:42:06.000Z","msg":"因航用手機登機證就得"},{"pid":"b347717306234c809a41b1964a40dd0f110fb658","tid":760140,"uid":172825,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f0afa0dbfad9da65a45ce2f8dea9c8b3b3a0b813","tid":760140,"uid":89240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T09:25:46.000Z","msg":"如果唔bag drop <br />\n拎住個qr code就直入<br />\n臨上機前俾佢望下本passport就得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T11:44:57.000Z","msg":"唔係，如果冇埋到check in櫃檯，入到禁區閘口要去到閘口櫃檯比地勤人員更新證件，先可以入去，唔係話show 下passport就得<br />\n<br />\n利申 做緊地勤"},{"pid":"0a67850a6aced7b54984b294568b7ff7b1665c35","tid":760140,"uid":21407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b347717306234c809a41b1964a40dd0f110fb658","tid":760140,"uid":172825,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"q